==Finnish==
===Verb===
# [[vituttaa]]
===Usage notes===
Like the word ''vituttaa'', this word normally indicates the user as the person in question.
*''Mua kyrpii.'' I'm deeply annoyed. Literally: It cocks me.
*''Kyrpii niin vitusti.'' I'm so fucking deeply annoyed. Literally: It cocks me like fuck. 
*''Mua alkaa pikkuhiljaa kyrpiä.'' I'm slowly getting deeply annoyed. Literally: It's slowly starting to cock me. Please note here just about the only case where the verb is used in the plain form ''kyrpiä''.

